info.invgens.inventory_furnace_generator: Generates Redstone Flux from burnable items in generator slot. Can recharge items in inventory (including armor and curios slots).
info.invgens.inventory_culinary_generato: Generates Redstone Flux from food items placed in generator slot. Can recharge items in inventory (including armor and curios slots).
info.invgens.inventory_death_generator: Generates Redstone Flux from undead mob items in generator slot. Can recharge items in inventory (including armor and curios slots).
info.invgens.inventory_end_generator: Generates Redstone Flux from ender pearl and ender eye items in generator slot. Can recharge items in inventory (including armor and curios slots).
info.invgens.inventory_explosive_generat: Generates Redstone Flux from gunpowder and tnt items in generator slot. Can recharge items in inventory (including armor and curios slots).
info.invgens.inventory_frosty_generator: Generates Redstone Flux from cold items in generator slot. Can recharge items in inventory (including armor and curios slots).
info.invgens.inventory_halitosis_generat: Generates Redstone Flux from dragon's breath items in generator slot. Can recharge items in inventory (including armor and curios slots).
info.invgens.inventory_magmatic_generato: Generates Redstone Flux from lava bucket items in generator slot. Can recharge items in inventory (including armor and curios slots).
info.invgens.inventory_nether_star_gener: Generates Redstone Flux from nether star items in generator slot. Can recharge items in inventory (including armor and curios slots).
info.invgens.inventory_overclocked_gener: Generates Redstone Flux from burnable items in generator slot at an extremely fast rate. Can recharge items in inventory (including armor and curios slots).
info.invgens.inventory_pink_generator: Generates Redstone Flux from pink items in generator slot. Can recharge items in inventory (including armor and curios slots).
info.invgens.inventory_potion_generator: Generates Redstone Flux from potion items in generator slot. Can recharge items in inventory (including armor and curios slots).
info.invgens.inventory_slimey_generator: Generates Redstone Flux from slime items in generator slot. Can recharge items in inventory (including armor and curios slots).
info.invgens.inventory_survivalist_gener: Generates Redstone Flux from burnable items in generator slot, capped at 5 RF/t. Can recharge items in inventory (including armor and curios slots).
info.invgens.auto_pull_upgrade: When an item is picked up it will automatically go in the inventory generator slot if valid.
info.invgens.no_effect_upgrade: Removes effects applied by the inventory generator.
info.invgens.speed_upgrade: Increases the RF/t produced but fuels are burned faster.
